									В.</name></author><title>A History of Aesthetics</title>, <pubPlace>L.</pubPlace>, <date>1892</date></bibl>;</item><item>,<bibl><author><name type="person" key="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benedetto_Croce">С r о с е В.</name></author>,
